          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Amos 7:12",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". And such he may be called, either because he really had the gift of prophecy or because as the name of prophets is sometimes given to those who had not prophetical gifts, but were only officers and minsters devoted to and employed in God’s worship and service, as ",
        "children": []
