        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Dost thou see",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "? i.e. understand: an untenable rendering. (3) The Vulg. gives different vowels to the consonants, and renders, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "O seer, return",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", &c. (4) The Sept. reads, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "See! thou shalt return",
        "children": []
      },
      {
